# copilot-instructions.md

## GitHub Copilot Usage Instructions

- Use Copilot suggestions as a starting point, not as final code.
- Always review and test Copilot-generated code before committing.
- Ensure all code follows the project's style and contribution guidelines.
- Do not accept or commit any code that includes sensitive data, credentials, or proprietary information.
- Add comments or documentation to clarify Copilot-generated code where necessary.
- If unsure about a suggestion, ask for a review from another team member.
- Refer to [CONTRIBUTING.md](./CONTRIBUTING.md) for general contribution practices.

---